                  <li class="hidden-xs">
                    <a class="js-sharearticle" target="_blank" href="mailto:?subject=Live%20updates%3A%20Michael%20Cohen%20testimony%20before%20Congress%20on%20NBCNews.com&body=From%20NBCNews.com... %0D%0A%0D%0A%20Live%20updates%3A%20Michael%20Cohen%20testimony%20before%20Congress%0D%0Ahttps://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/live-blog/live-updates-michael-cohen-testimony-congress-n976196?cid=eml_onsite
