                            <h2 class="nbcnews-dc-heading"><a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/card/thank-you-good-night-n977456">Thank you, and good night.</a></h2>
                          </header>
                      <div itemprop="articleBody">
                                          <p> We're closing down our live blog for the evening. Thanks for staying with us today. If you missed any part of the action, catch up by scrolling down through the blog for key moments, fiery exchanges and real-time analysis. </p>
                                          <p> Watch the highlights below, or check out the best lines from the hearing <a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/politics-news/michael-cohen-testimony-10-best-lines-his-hearing-congress-n977116" target="_blank">here</a>. See you all next time.  </p>
