                          <header class="nbcnews-dc-header cf">
                            <h2 class="nbcnews-dc-heading"><a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/card/cohen-says-he-hasn-t-seen-proof-trump-s-tax-n977341">Cohen says he hasn&#x27;t seen proof Trump&#x27;s tax returns are under audit</a></h2>
                          </header>
                      <div itemprop="articleBody">
                                          <p> Cohen said that he didn't actually think Trump's tax returns were under audit during the 2016 election, contrary to what Trump has long claimed.  </p>
                                          <p> "I asked for a copy of the audit so that I could use it in terms of my statements to the press. And I was never able to obtain one," he said in answer to a question about whether Trump's tax returns were, in fact, under audit by the IRS.  </p>
                                          <p> Trump refused to release his tax returns while running for office because he said they were under audit. He has never released them. </p>
                                          <p> Trump is the only major party nominee of the past 40 years to not release his tax returns. </p>
                      </div>
